msg: This patch effectively reverts HTTPCLIENT-643 changes. Multihome fail-over mechanism simply cannot be properly implemented at the socket factory level. A failure in the connect method can leave the socket in a inconsistent state on some platforms (Mac OS), making it impossible to connect the same socket to a different address
